description: This dataset shows points of interest in Slovakia. Features included in this dataset include, libraries, post offices, places of worship, parking, restaurants, cafes, fuel, parking, police, theaters, cinemas, prisons, universities, camp sites and other public places. there are over 2,000 points of interest included.
